<HEAD>05-10-88 23:50</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By The Associated Press</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
 Here are the latest, unofficial results in the Republican presidential primaries on Tuesday.
</TEXT>
<HEAD>NEBRASKA</HEAD>
<TEXT>
 1,490 of 1,870 precincts reporting - 80 percent <PERSON> Bush </PERSON>, 95,154 - 72 percent <PERSON> Robertson </PERSON>, 6,784 - 5 percent <PERSON> Dole </PERSON>, 30,565 - 23 percent
</TEXT>
